switchblock for Debian
-----------------
After you install the package,
0) make sure memlockd is enabled
1) write a valid /etc/switchblocktab
2) replace UUIDs with /dev/mapper/... in /etc/fstab
3) update-initramfs to incorporate switchblocktab
4) update-grub to fix root=... kernel parameter
5) reboot
